Sent: Tuesday, November 9, 2021 7:33 AM 
To 
(USANYS) 
Subject: letter referencing Ghislaine Maxwell 
Colleagues, 
My office received the attached email as citizen correspondence. Because it references Jeffrey Epstein and 
Ghislaine Maxwell, I am forwarding it to you for whatever consideration you deem appropriate. Consistent 
with our standard response, we will simply advise the writer to contact the FBI. Please let me know if you have 
any questions. Thanks very much, 
Deputy Chief for Policy and Legislation 
Child Exploitation and Obscenity Section 
U.S. Department of Justice 
(mobile) 
EFTA00010130
